name: [Flyer Template] Room Hunting - Analog Edition (Community)
description:
🏚 Today's housing crisis is a result of rapid population growth and a lack of supply.


👀 However, there are still plenty of people out there who have a house / spare room, yet don't list them online.


✨ With this template, you can take the room hunt in your hands, support your local print shop, raise local awareness and find those people without the use of social media or overly competitive online communities / housing portals.
